Results.ReviewText: We really like this coffee in our household, it melts immediately in hot water and taste delicious on it's own or with milk. The taste of this is superior to any other granulated instant coffee.
Results.Title: Smooth and creamy

Results.ReviewText: I bought this as it looked 'inviting' on the shelf. I was really surprised just how smooth it is. All my friends really love it. I appear to have now turned into the 'local coffee and chat Cafe'
Results.Title: I was really surprised,

Results.ReviewText:
I have been using this for months now and finally REALLY enjoy a cup of coffee!

Coffee is the one thing I won't skimp on but Nescafe is a great coffee but always available at a great price!!
Results.Title: Smooth and a great aroma and flavour!

Results.ReviewText: I've been using this for some time now and find the taste and quality very consistent.  It looks and tastes like freshly brewed coffee - I now mostly use it instead of bothering to brew fresh.
Results.Title: Tastes like freshly brewed coffee!

Results.ReviewText: Favourite coffee, but why is it so hard to find, so many shops do not sell it, I have to go out of my way to buy it at the one shop that I know that sells it, the large Sainsbury's in Hessle.
Results.Title: Creamy

Results.ReviewText: I buy Nescafe Gold Crema every week for home use and I also buy it for work.  It has a lovely smooth tast and is so creamy.  It is just the right strength too, not too weak, not too strong.
Results.Title: My favourite coffee

Results.ReviewText: I have just discovered Crema and I have to say it is one of the nicest , smoothest, rich flavoured coffees I have ever tried.  I love the strong taste with the Crema texture.  I love it!!
Results.Title: Perfect cup of coffee every time

Results.ReviewText: I bought this yesterday for the first time and I thought it tasted lovely! Smooth & Silky - I absolutely love it and I would definitely recommend it to all who love a nice smooth coffee.
Results.Title: Fantastic tasting and smooth.

Results.ReviewText: This is the best coffee ever. Beautiful flavour, and so smooth. Not for strong coffee drinkers, just perfect for me. Also makes the most wonderful lattés. Definitely gets 5stars from me.
Results.Title: GORGEOUS

Results.ReviewText: Bought this expecting to be just like normal dried coffee. Wow. I was so wrong. Nice velvety smooth coffee and strong distinctive taste. So much better than the leading coffee baristas .
Results.Title: My new favourite

Results.ReviewText: I'm not one for drinking instant coffee but I bought this when I had workmen doing some work & tried a cup myself & absolutely loved it. It's very smooth & creamy & has a lovely flavour
Results.Title: Deliciously smooth

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe gold crema is delicious normally I drink Nescafe instant but thought I would try crema.  So pleased I made the change it tastes so good, sat back and thought I gone to heaven!!!
Results.Title: heaven in a cup

Results.ReviewText: I bought this about 3 weeks ago, i absolutely love this coffee, its probably the best coffee i have ever tasted, smooth, creamy, amazing aroma, lovely taste. Itnis just amazing quality
Results.Title: Amazing coffee

Results.ReviewText: I came across this in Asda, I normally drink normal gold blend instant but thought I'd give this a try. Wow! Just like what you get at a coffee shop but instant. Thank you gold blend
Results.Title: Best out there

Results.ReviewText: I was given a Nescafe Gold Crema by a friend whilst visiting her and now I put it my weekly shop, very nice for a change from my normal Nescafe original which is my everyday go to.
Results.Title: Me Time

Results.ReviewText: I haven't been able to drink coffee for months due to my health, but this coffee was worth waiting for....I love it. It's so smooth and creamy and not too strong. Excellent coffee!
Results.Title: Smooth & creamy

Results.ReviewText: I love this but have been unable to get it in Morrisons. The nicest, flavoursome but not harsh coffee. Will go looking in a different store. Nearly out of it and can't have that!
Results.Title: crema

Results.ReviewText: I purchased a few months ago and I will now not consume any other brand of coffee.  There is the right amount of flavour and creaminess. Feels like a treat each time a have a cup
Results.Title: Recommend

Results.ReviewText: Bought this on offer from Waitrose from my usual Gold Blend and pleased I did. It dissolves easily and makes a creamy, frothy lovely tasting coffee. Would recommend to a friend x
Results.Title: Creamy and frothy

Results.ReviewText: I liked the initial taste but I found that soon disappeared, I think if you added a longer lasting richness to this coffee it would surpass some other brands twice the price!
Results.Title: Could have more depth

Results.ReviewText: purchased this product, normally buy nescafe gold blend anyway, but the crema makes a really delicious different cup of coffee. its very tasteful and one cup is not enough!.
Results.Title: eye catching

Results.ReviewText: Bought this from the local supermarket. A little sceptical at first, but very creamy and  an excellent choice. This will be sat on my shelve next to the Nescafe Gold Blend!
Results.Title: Very Very Tasty!!

Results.ReviewText: A really nice, well rounded, smooth and tasty coffee for the price. Did create a small bit of crema on the top of my coffee, but nothing like when using a coffee machine.
Results.Title: Nice coffee!

Results.ReviewText: Have been looking for a super smooth coffee for a while and it looks like I've found my perfect match!  Sooo smooth, its quite simply luxurious.  Would highly recommend.
Results.Title: Soooo smooth it's dreamy!

Results.ReviewText: My beloved coffee machine stopped working so bought this product, was really amazed at the quality and closeness  to machine coffee, am not replacing the coffee machine!
Results.Title: surprisingly good

Results.ReviewText: I used to buy the Nescafe Azera but after tasting the new Crema, I now have a new favourite instant coffee.  It is delicious - smooth, creamy, rich and feels indulgent.
Results.Title: Creamy smooth coffee in a jar!

Results.ReviewText: I knew I should not have bought this... I absolutely love it on my third jar now and have also got my daughter drinking it who has never been a great fan of hot drinks
Results.Title: Loved it! too much....

Results.ReviewText: This was my favourite,till all the stores in DUMFRIES stopped stocking it .I thought it had been discontinued,so this is great news ,if TESCO & MORRISONS will sell it
Results.Title: Nescafé at its Best

Results.ReviewText: I bought this product recently and was really pleased with the wonderful flavour. It was so much better than other brands. The flavour was rich and creamy.  Loved it!
Results.Title: Perfect!

Results.ReviewText: I tried this instead of my usual brand and it had such a luxurious velvety taste it is going to replace my usual brand. My coffee and walnut cake is enhanced as well.
Results.Title: Gold class in a coffee cup
